title: 服务器安装authme出错
txt_content:
authme下载最新版没用就拿了上个版本，加了Authme后服务端一直重启，想知道怎么把这个插件安装上面报错

[14:14:58] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] Enabling AuthMe v5.4.0-b1877*
[14:14:59] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] SQLite Setup finished
[14:14:59] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] Hooked into PermissionsEx!
[14:14:59] [Server thread/WARN]: [AuthMe] Aborting initialization of AuthMe: [InjectorReflectionException]: Could not invoke constructor of class 'class fr.xephi.authme.command.CommandHandler'
[14:14:59] [Server thread/WARN]: [AuthMe] THE SERVER IS GOING TO SHUT DOWN AS DEFINED IN THE CONFIGURATION!
[14:14:59] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] Waiting for 0 tasks to finish
[14:14:59] [Server thread/INFO]: [AuthMe] AuthMe 5.4.0-b1877 disabled!


服务端版本1.14.4  Spigot
